{"tid":1413921,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"匯控全球裁員4750人 只要針對高層","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T11:44:00.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b7423a1f6f97d238ec5d67e6fa3dc1027c1ad3","tid":1413921,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"匯控(00005)宣布范寧已退任集團行政總裁及董事職位後，《華爾街日報》引述消息人士指，該集團將裁員最多2%。以該行全球237,685名員工計算，即裁員約4,750人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，匯控財務董事邵偉信Ewen Stevenson在一次採訪中表示，裁員行動將針對高層員工，削減該行4%的員工工資成本。集團指，今年遣散成本將高達6.5億至7億美元。<br />\n<br />\n受中美貿易摩擦等緊張局勢影響，部分客戶的貿易及投資有限，集團指出，由於包括美國降息在內的不利因素，明年美國業務的有形資產回報率將難以達到6%的目標。"},{"pid":"a4d630407934cf364a2333fe2e3f558f24d214c0","tid":1413921,"uid":193258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c756722c84c6aca419357a19724f2d6d959193","tid":1413921,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">200%令政府中央收皮(和平合法易過長期罷工)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412496</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"afed69d59c5dcc1ee4a049cdcddde4a60cf58935","tid":1413921,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 德銀法興之後...."}]}